WEBVTT

00:00:01.142 --> 00:00:02.351
Roznboym.

00:00:02.188 --> 00:00:04.139
Roznbaum-Zeydner.

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:11.075
iz hot ir gezolt zayn in di dire in Vlokho tsuzamen mitn man un mit nokh yemen?

00:00:09.124 --> 00:00:14.715
m- m- m- un mit nokh eymen. un er hot gegebn a s- er hot gehat a sakh gelt, er iz gevezn a shmugler.

00:00:14.715 --> 00:00:17.690
nor undz ho'mir nisht gekukt. vet zayn nokh eyner.

00:00:17.713 --> 00:00:25.638
hot men gekoyft a shtub mit a kekh, mit bakvemlekhkeytn, a forgeshritene azoy azoy vi eygntum kimat.

00:00:26.961 --> 00:00:33.621
bin ikh dortn gevezn eyner aleyn, zi iz avekgegangen tsu der arbet, s'geven vinter,

00:00:34.875 --> 00:00:37.248
un der zun iz oykh avek oyf arbet,

00:00:34.909 --> 00:00:41.788
vinter, SLICHA, eyn moment, dos iz geven vinter fun nayntsn dray un fertsik shoyn?

00:00:41.693 --> 00:00:43.779
tsvey un fertsik nokh alts.

00:00:42.638 --> 00:00:45.501
nokh tsvey un fertsik, OK.

00:00:44.359 --> 00:00:48.234
yo. dos iz nokh geven tsvey un fertsik.

00:00:48.308 --> 00:00:52.639
vayl sof tsvey un fertsik bin ikh shoyn tsurikgegangen.

00:00:51.362 --> 00:00:53.178
tsurikgekumen, OK.

00:00:53.100 --> 00:00:55.811
tsurikgegangen tsu mayn man oyf Leshno.

00:00:56.813 --> 00:01:03.590
y- zeks vokhn bin ikh dortn geven, zi flegt avekgeyn, ikh bin mit ir geshlofn in eyn UNK bet.

00:01:03.597 --> 00:01:05.987
un un der zun iz geshlofn in kekh.

00:01:07.596 --> 00:01:12.737
ikh a- ikh hob gornisht gehat UNK, nor ikh bin dokh gelegn in bet, keyner iz dokh nisht geven.

00:01:12.844 --> 00:01:16.803
in BET-KISE bin ikh nisht gegangen kedey nisht aroystsulozn dos vaser.

00:01:17.620 --> 00:01:22.913
di baderfenishn hob ikh gemakht in a tsaytung, ikh ken dokh redn az er farshteyt dokh nisht,

00:01:23.121 --> 00:01:31.620
un arayngerukt in di ferte fayerke, ikh zol nisht lozn aroplozn dos vaser, s'zol nisht hern.

00:01:31.845 --> 00:01:38.398
un s'gevezn fintster, s'iz zumer vinter f- falt dokh tsu shnel v- shnel nakht,

00:01:38.398 --> 00:01:40.884
iz geven farhongen di fentsters.

00:01:40.907 --> 00:01:47.854
nor ikh hob ongetsundn KHASHMAL, un ikh hob opgesheylt kartofles, bay nakht hot es gekokht. ho'mir ale gegesn.

00:01:49.817 --> 00:01:56.038
s'iz shoyn gevezn, s'mir shoyn nimes gevorn, do mayn man kumt nisht, s'punkt geven a shtile tsayt.

00:01:56.145 --> 00:01:58.673
nokhn kotsho iz dos gevezn.

00:01:58.673 --> 00:02:05.896
iz geven shtil, zey hobn nisht gemakht keyn selektsyes, di vos hobn gearbet, tsi in a bekeray, tsi vu, zenen iz geven shtil.

00:02:05.896 --> 00:02:10.314
zey hobn nisht genumen keynemen aroystsushikn. s'geven shtil.

00:02:10.978 --> 00:02:16.001
zog ikh, un do gey kumt er nisht, mayn man, un ikh veys nisht oyb, zog ikh,

00:02:16.412 --> 00:02:24.061
hob ikh genumen, ikh bin arayngeforn keyn Varshe, dos heyst oyf Leshno, oyf di arbet. nisht in mayn dire, mayn dire hob ikh mer nisht ongezen far mayne oygn

00:02:24.061 --> 00:02:27.138
zint ikh hob ir de- zikh ikh hob ir ibergelozt.

00:02:26.892 --> 00:02:28.793
ir zent avek fun di froy.

00:02:28.849 --> 00:02:34.718
yo. alz- REGA, vu ikh hob nisht aropgelozt afile keyn vaser.

00:02:34.718 --> 00:02:42.461
iz zi gekumen fun der arbet, zogt der zogt der goy, "emetser iz do bay aykh, s'iz lekhtik."

00:02:42.889 --> 00:02:50.209
vayzt oys nokh a shpare, vos iz geven bay di goyim oykh farhongen, vayl far far zey hobn moyre gehat far bombardirungen,

00:02:50.209 --> 00:02:54.594
un s'geven farhongen mit a kots, nor vayzt oys s- m'hot gezen a bisl likht.

00:02:54.972 --> 00:03:00.444
un do hob ikh shoyn nisht gekent mer oyshaltn eyner aleyn, nisht gevust vos mitn kind.

00:03:00.444 --> 00:03:03.740
yo, dos kind hobn zey etlekhe mol gebrengt.

00:03:04.455 --> 00:03:05.951
hot bin ikh az,

00:03:04.675 --> 00:03:07.014
dort ahin keyn Vokhe?

00:03:06.447 --> 00:03:10.080
yo. UNK dokh geven a mishpokhe, a shvester fun i- fun ir,

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:13.900
hot er ir ayngeredt, azoy vi du bist azoy orem, k- on a man,

00:03:13.900 --> 00:03:19.640
darfst arbetn shver, yetst hostu nisht keyn dire, dos shtikl shtub darfstu avekgebn dem yingstn zun,

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:24.904
un du mit dem tsveytn darfst oykhet hobn, un du kenst fardinen un shoyn.

00:03:24.904 --> 00:03:32.110
zi oyf z- ir nomen hot zi genumen di shtub, s'geven azoy vi a BAYIT MESHUTAF, azoy vi a SHIKUN. in Narozhne.

00:03:32.110 --> 00:03:36.208
s'iz Pilsudskego nayntsn gevezn.

00:03:38.037 --> 00:03:42.995
ikh bin bamiest gevorn, ikh hob shoyn mer nisht gehat keyn gedult tsu zayn dort, keyn bikhl, gornisht

00:03:42.995 --> 00:03:46.335
iz dort geven, vayl zi hot zikh dokh nor vos arayngetsoygn, zi hot gornisht farmogt.

00:03:46.335 --> 00:03:53.505
zi iz geven zeyer a oreme. un oysgezen hot zi azoy vi tsen yidishe. un ikh nisht un zi yo. a shvartsinke gevezn.

00:03:54.102 --> 00:04:02.111
un a froy a gelitene, un hot gearbet bay shvartser arbet, on a man, a man geven UNK, a voyler yung, ikh veys nisht.

00:04:02.320 --> 00:04:03.596
ikh hob im nisht gekent.

00:04:03.805 --> 00:04:13.164
alzo, ikh hob bashlosn, azoy vi, kumt zi aroyf, ven zogt zi, ot zogt er der der str- der vos hot gehitn dos hoyz,

00:04:16.039 --> 00:04:24.268
"emetser iz do bay dir UNK. UNK", zogt er, "UNK, far vos brent di di di elektrye?"

00:04:26.502 --> 00:04:32.801
zi hot mir dos ot gezogt, un mir iz es gekrokhn in kop arayn, mir iz shoyn geven farmiest fun zeks vokhn eyner aleyn.

00:04:32.801 --> 00:04:40.552
optsulign a gantser tog. bin a biz zi kumt, dernokh dem est men dos bisl esn,

00:04:41.385 --> 00:04:46.985
zog ikh, ikh vel arayn, azoy vi s'shtil, un gehat grisn hob ikh az s'iz dervayl nishto keyn bombardirungen,

00:04:46.985 --> 00:04:51.905
m'makht nisht m'zidlt nisht oys keynem, un di vos zey arbetn arbetn, vos zenen geblibn,

00:04:51.905 --> 00:04:58.170
nokh kotsho iz geven shtil a por monatn. zog ikh, ikh vel arayngeyn.

00:04:58.530 --> 00:05:03.367
un efsher vel ikh im ibertsaygn, vet men tsurik ahin, oder ikh veys, m'vet zen vos vet zayn.

00:05:03.660 --> 00:05:06.252
alzo ikh bin gekumen tsurik oyf Lashno,

00:05:06.748 --> 00:05:11.011
hob ikh gehert a grus fun vemenem, dakht zikh fun mayn bruder,

00:05:11.288 --> 00:05:15.264
az oyf oyf mayn gas vu ikh hob gehat mayn dire,

00:05:16.266 --> 00:05:23.263
vo- voynt eyner a retsitator, s'iz geven Grosbard, a yidisher retsitator, ir veyst vos heyst retsitator?

00:05:23.404 --> 00:05:30.586
er er deklamirt poezye, heyst a retsitator. iz geven Grosbard bay undz in yidish.

00:05:30.711 --> 00:05:35.599
n- yener vos m'hot gevoynt mit im tsuzamen oyf zumer voynung,

00:05:36.567 --> 00:05:41.168
iz nisht gekumen, yener hot ge- s- s'iz nisht geven zayn parnose, er iz geven raykh.

00:05:41.275 --> 00:05:45.836
az er gefint zikh oyf Lesh- oyf oyf Shtsheshlive vu ikh hob gevoynt,

00:05:45.836 --> 00:05:48.831
di gas heyst Shtshelive, heyst a gliklekhe gas.

00:05:48.831 --> 00:05:55.308
SZCZESLIWA, iz a gliklekhe, SZCZESLIWA, a froy, un di gas iz hot geheysn SZCZESLIWA.

00:05:57.222 --> 00:06:05.715
az dortn o er arbet in a in a BET-SEFER iz gevezn a gas derlebn iz gevezn oykh a bisl arbet oyfn ETAR,

00:06:05.715 --> 00:06:10.834
er iz ⟨niber⟩ dort basheftikt. ober der vos ikh zog, er iz geven aza retsitator a guter,

00:06:10.941 --> 00:06:15.001
hot hot geh- iz geven raykh, er hot gehat a gesheft fun farbn,

00:06:15.008 --> 00:06:20.717
azoy az er hot nisht badorfn zayn aroystretn far keyn gelt, hot men nisht azoy gevust fun im.

00:06:20.717 --> 00:06:24.460
nor ikh bin a kenerin, aleyn sheyn retsitirt, un a yidish

00:06:24.477 --> 00:06:31.077
ken ikh dokh dem rikhtikn vos ale. di aktsent iz nor fun Varshe, ober ikh ken dokh dem rikhtikn yidish,

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:36.923
s'nisht azanes nokh geboyrn gevorn. Ostrovski hot er geheysn, Shloyme Ostrovski.

00:06:37.772 --> 00:06:45.343
hot men gevoynt dem z- z- zumer take tsuzamen oykhet derlebn in a vilye, ven m'iz geven oyf oyf Le- oyf zumer voynung.

00:06:45.889 --> 00:06:51.519
zog ikh, ikh vel geyn ahin un ikh vel mikh khapn un zen tsi m'ho- tsi s'iz epes do in undzer voynung.

00:06:52.318 --> 00:06:55.023
bin iz ot darf men geyn a groysn veg

00:06:55.023 --> 00:06:59.653
vos iz geven gantsn toyt, nisht bavoynt, nokh gants Zamenhof oysgeyn.

00:07:00.182 --> 00:07:04.811
un nokh a shtikl gas fun Zamenhof fun Leshno UNK adurkhgeyn.

00:07:04.811 --> 00:07:10.962
un ikh bin ongekumen, ikh bin durkhgeganen besholem. ikh bin ongekumen oyf oyf Shtsheshlive, dort oyf di gas vu ikh hob gevoynt,

00:07:10.962 --> 00:07:17.777
ikh hob gevoynt elef, un er hot gevoynt, tsulib der arbet hot er dort gevoynt, er hot gearbet derlebn oyf Stavke.

00:07:18.002 --> 00:07:24.628
iz iz far far di daytshn. iz mit di mishpokhe iz er gevezn.

00:07:25.647 --> 00:07:28.729
un zog ikh ikh vel eyn mol gebn a kuk vos tut zikh.

00:07:29.359 --> 00:07:32.458
un ikh hob gevoynt in tsveytn hoyf, s'geven tsvey heyf,

00:07:32.464 --> 00:07:37.894
un in mitn iz oykh geshtanen a gebayde, un ikh hob gevoynt in tsveytn hoyf oyfn fertn shtok.

00:07:37.894 --> 00:07:46.801
nor s'geven topele fentsters, s'geven fun in ayngeboytete, m'hot shoyn nisht badorfn oyfmakhn di lift- di ⟨liftishkes⟩ UNK arayn, s'nisht vikhtik shoyn dos alding.

00:07:47.331 --> 00:07:56.572
un ikh hey- ikh nem eyn mol di froy zayne, un m'geyt arop, zog ikh, kum, m'vet zen vos bay mir in shtub tut zikh, tsi s'voynt ver s- ver do, tsi s'iz epes a lebn.

00:07:56.848 --> 00:08:02.495
ikh kum arayn, un vil arayngeyn in tsveytn hoyf arayn, ligt aza hoykhe kupe mist,

00:08:02.502 --> 00:08:10.680
un a bild vos iz gevorn gemale- vos ikh bin geven gemoln, az hekher vi d- vi a vi a tir, vi di tir.

00:08:11.209 --> 00:08:19.016
fun Hendeln, fun di barimte, fun Ida Hendel's tate. er bay im hot men hob ikh pozirt,

00:08:19.039 --> 00:08:25.887
vayl maynem mayne shviger-eltern hob im gemakht a a plashtsh,

00:08:25.887 --> 00:08:32.752
un an antsug, er zol hobn mit vos tsu forn mit di Yida oyf aroystretn keyn Tshekhotshinek, s'geven a kur-ort.

00:08:32.826 --> 00:08:40.037
un er hot nisht gehat vos ontsutun. geven iz er aleyn fun Khelm, ale zenen ge- ale di kinder oykhet, alts fun Khelm.

00:08:40.037 --> 00:08:46.843
un arayn keyn Varshe hot er gevoynt kle- in a klener shtibele vi mayn kokh, mit tsvey oyfleyg betlekh.

00:08:46.950 --> 00:08:52.457
azoy az tsu makhn zikh an ontsutun iz nisht gevezn, s'koym geven tsu esn.

00:08:52.457 --> 00:09:02.605
un zi di Yida hot gekrign Vinyafski's fidl kontsert hot zi gekrign di premye, di shenste. Vinyafski's fidl kontsert.

00:09:03.100 --> 00:09:08.927
hot zi ongehoybn krign bashtelungen, a klal hot er gehat a bashtelung keyn Tshekhotshinik tsu forn, hot er nisht gehat in vos.

00:09:08.927 --> 00:09:16.335
hobn mayne shviger-eltern im gemakht a iz ge- az er zol mir, mayn shviger iz avekgeforn iz geshtorbn in Lublin,

00:09:16.335 --> 00:09:24.711
un un nokh a por vokhn, bay tsvey un fertsik yor, un zi hot es bashtelt take. hot zi gezogt azoy, zol es zol es dervayle hengen iber mayn bet.

00:09:25.088 --> 00:09:28.592
un makhts im, zol er hobn mit vos tsu forn mit Yiditshka.

00:09:29.070 --> 00:09:32.186
ikh hob im pozirt azoy nokh oykh bay a tishl,

00:09:32.766 --> 00:09:39.375
vayl s'gevezn dort geven a pitsl shtibl, s'geven oyfsh- oyfleyg betlekh. zeks vokhn.

00:09:40.157 --> 00:09:46.614
yedn tog, un zi hot dervayl geshpilt, un er hot, tomer zi hot gemakht epes shlekhts, hot er, er hot oykh geshpilt,

00:09:46.924 --> 00:09:50.850
hot er gemakht mitn fus, un er hot arop geshtekt, un zi hot farbesert zikh.

00:09:52.273 --> 00:09:57.819
ikh kum dort zen mayn dire, geb a kuk oyf di kupe mist in der heykh ligt dos bild.

00:09:58.517 --> 00:10:00.825
bin ikh shoyn aroyfgeganen in shtub arayn.

00:10:00.825 --> 00:10:07.944
ikh hob dokh say vi nisht gehat bedeye tsu, do hot men dokh nisht gekent zayn, s'dokh gevezn oysern geto, oyser arbet, oyser alding.

00:10:07.967 --> 00:10:15.589
s'dokh gevezn noent fun di umshlag-plats un, azoy az ikh bin tsurikgegan- ikh bin geblibn.

00:10:15.595 --> 00:10:21.376
ikh bin geblibn, bin ikh geblibn biz biz nay-yor, biz dray un fertsik.

00:10:22.092 --> 00:10:26.305
er der der litsitator vos ikh zog aykh,

00:10:26.631 --> 00:10:34.336
geyt arop tsu der arbet in dem hoyz fun vos m'hot gelernt a fakhlayt,

00:10:34.461 --> 00:10:39.466
oyf in lebn Balta gas, un zogt, s'tut zikh dort khurbm!

00:10:40.401 --> 00:10:46.301
s'kumen for shiserayen o- epes oyf Nisko oyf vu, nu Rute geyt arop zen.

00:10:46.425 --> 00:10:51.768
ikh kum arop, ikh tref take dem vos er hot gezolt mit undz kumen in di dire voynen.

00:10:52.095 --> 00:10:59.120
un der oyle- vos iz gevezn? zey vos zenen hobn gearbet, hobn gehert a for arayn in mitn der nakht.

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:05.049
nisht azoy vi s'biz yetst geven sh- biz yetst shtil biz tsum kes- nokhn kesl.

00:11:06.439 --> 00:11:09.875
un zey hobn zikh tsugegreyt, zey hobn shoyn gehat a bisl gever.

00:11:10.270 --> 00:11:16.406
un zey hobn ge- un zey un zey hobn gevust, zey hot zey hobn gehert a tuperay, a foreray fun mototsiklen,

00:11:17.374 --> 00:11:23.341
zenen zey aroys vifl zey hobn gekent fun gantsn gegnt vos iz gevezn, vos hobn gehat dos bisl gever,

00:11:23.348 --> 00:11:26.602
un zey hobn ongehoybn sh- zey hobn bashlosn tsu shteln a vidershtand.

00:11:26.602 --> 00:11:30.767
dervayle hot men opgeshikt a gresere khevre, m'hot zey epes ale tseyogt,

00:11:30.874 --> 00:11:33.790
un ikh hob opgeratevet dem take vos

00:11:34.575 --> 00:11:41.426
vem ikh hob nor gekent gevisn fun di gas fun Niske vu m'ken ariber krikhn oyf oyf Nile,

00:11:41.426 --> 00:11:43.307
vu dort iz shoyn gevezn shtil.

00:11:43.307 --> 00:11:48.283
s'iz gevezn, ikh hob nisht gekent geyn tsurik, s'iz geven a por tog, a dray fir tog

00:11:48.390 --> 00:11:55.184
oysnam tsushtand, m'hot nisht getort aroysgeyn in gantsn, un azoy vi m'hot gekent aroysgeyn bin ikh tsurikgegangen oyf Leshno tsu mayn man.

00:11:55.866 --> 00:11:58.205
un dos iz geven in ra- dray un f-

00:11:57.520 --> 00:12:02.289
d- dos iz shoyn geven in dray un fertsik yanuar, akhtstn yanuar, dos gedenk ikh.

00:12:03.915 --> 00:12:06.069
ikh gede- ikh hob alts, ikh hob,

00:12:03.915 --> 00:12:08.296
iz demolts iz geven an onheyb fun oyfshtand eygntlekh?

00:12:07.408 --> 00:12:11.952
dos iz gevezn a pruv antkegn tsu shteln zikh, nisht keyn oyfshtand.

00:12:11.952 --> 00:12:17.409
dos heyst s'iz gevezn a a an entfer bloyz, a vidershtand.

00:12:18.968 --> 00:12:24.480
der o dos iz geven fun di mentshn vos hobn tsugegreyt dem dem oyfshtand.

00:12:25.026 --> 00:12:27.939
barn oyfshtand iz loyt mir

00:12:29.143 --> 00:12:33.845
gevezn nisht mer vi tsvontsik toyznt yidn, mit ale basheftikte.

00:12:34.678 --> 00:12:36.781
ir zent shoyn nisht geven dort.

00:12:35.910 --> 00:12:41.627
ikh bin dokh shoyn nisht geven fun lang. ikh bin dokh shoyn nisht gevezn fun kesl on in yenem gegnt.

00:12:37.733 --> 00:12:38.722
yo.

00:12:41.627 --> 00:12:47.497
nor yetst bin ikh gekumen zen az, ikh bin gekumen tsurik fun Vlokhi, funem shtub, yo.

00:12:45.090 --> 00:12:46.940
zen di dire.

00:12:47.475 --> 00:12:50.535
iz vos hot ir detsidirt tsu tun nokh dem?

00:12:51.300 --> 00:12:56.998
nokh dem iz gevezn shlekht, mayn man hot nisht gekent iberlozn ale,

00:12:57.763 --> 00:12:59.276
ver iz ale?

00:12:58.894 --> 00:13:01.717
di di shnayders, di gute shnayders.

00:13:01.717 --> 00:13:08.506
un m'hot dokh zey hobn nokh vi s'iz gearbet. alts bashtelungen, alts tayere zakhn.

00:13:08.648 --> 00:13:11.696
dos vos m'hot nisht gemakht in di shopn farn militer.

00:13:12.073 --> 00:13:19.391
nor dos iz gevezn azoy lapovke gegebn, kn- gegebn untergerukt. untergekoyft alding.

00:13:23.599 --> 00:13:27.626
ikh hob nisht gehat vos tsu tun derbay, mit zey,

00:13:29.117 --> 00:13:37.836
bin ikh aroys, hob ikh zikh farbundn mit dem Shevyitski un er hot shoyn gevoynt in di naye dire fun yidn oyf Shliske,

00:13:38.095 --> 00:13:45.497
hot er mikh nisht gehat vu tsu haltn, un ikh ho- s'geven fir tsimern, ober s'geven a mame zayner, un z- er un zi,

00:13:45.807 --> 00:13:53.631
un a zun, un a tokhter, un ir's a bruder, fun UNK, geharget gevorn in poylishn oyfshtand, der sheygets.

00:13:54.126 --> 00:14:00.937
un ikh hob nisht dortn gehat vu, bin ikh mit zey, hobn zey mikh koydem ikh bin gekumen, hobn zey mikh genumen tsu zikh in shlof-tsimer arayn.

00:14:01.230 --> 00:14:04.391
s'geven goldene parentshn fun a yid.

00:14:04.391 --> 00:14:11.231
s'geven farshidene antikn, iz bay mir iz gornisht, azelkhe shenklekh gantse, vos yidn hobn ibergelozt.

00:14:12.182 --> 00:14:23.026
er iz nisht gegangen rabeven. oder m'hot hot er es gekrign, oder di er hot zikh getoysht epes mit di yidn fun dort vos hobn gemuzt aroys, vayl er iz nisht gev- er iz geven genug ikh vey-

00:14:23.134 --> 00:14:26.253
ikh ikh zog nisht hundert protsent, ven m'hot tsu tun mit gelt,

00:14:26.253 --> 00:14:30.199
ober anshtendik, er hot dokh gegebn mir ale bakantshaftn.

00:14:30.694 --> 00:14:37.050
er hot eygntlekh geretet geratevet dos lebn fun ayer tokhter oykh un fun aykh, fun ale.

00:14:34.474 --> 00:14:39.834
fun ale, fun mir oykhet. ikh leb a dank im un mayn man hot oykh gekent lebn.

00:14:40.279 --> 00:14:48.097
vayl er hot nisht ge- afilek er hot oysgezen vi a goy er hot nisht gehat azan gutn aktsent oyf poylish, ober ergets hot men im gekent hal-

00:14:48.097 --> 00:14:52.760
mayn man hot gevolt tsunemen di shikse, a- azoy,

00:14:52.851 --> 00:14:59.325
vestlekh, veyst dokh in di antseger makht men dokh vestlekh, yo, bay antseger fun mener.

00:14:59.533 --> 00:15:03.074
dos hobn gearbet shikses. iz geve- ikh hob aykh shoyn dos dertseylt.

00:15:03.074 --> 00:15:07.391
iz shoyn eyn shikse vos hot gearbet arayn vestlekh, geven farlibt in mayn man.

00:15:07.482 --> 00:15:16.253
zi hot azoy gezogt, oyb zogst, un mayn man hot proklamirt shtendik az er iz link geshtimt, er iz a sotsya- a sotsyalist, a Trotskist, a dos,

00:15:16.253 --> 00:15:20.464
zogt zi, hot zi gezogt azoy. oyb, un zi iz geven a antisemitke,

00:15:20.464 --> 00:15:26.375
di vos hot aroysgenumen di vestlekh tsu neyen. dos hobn geneyt froyen, nisht keyn mener, vest- di vestn.

00:15:26.652 --> 00:15:35.128
iz hot zi hot zi ge- aroysgevizn genug antisemitishkeyt, un a yunge, a sheyne, mir iz geven interesant az men volt im opgeratevet.

00:15:35.128 --> 00:15:36.635
zi hot im zeyer lib gehat.

00:15:36.675 --> 00:15:41.295
a klal iz ge- ven er hot, koydem hot zi nisht gevust tsi er iz a yid, nor er hot oyfgemakht

00:15:41.295 --> 00:15:45.475
dos moyl, hot men gekent zen az der poylish iz nisht keyn, iz nisht azoy vi di polyakn redn.

00:15:45.475 --> 00:15:48.555
nor zi iz dokh, er iz dokh geven der der geber nor fun der arbet,

00:15:48.555 --> 00:15:52.795
hot zi gehat far im respekt, er hot a gute batsiung, un er tsu ir oykhet.

00:15:53.044 --> 00:16:00.884
hot zi gezogt azoy, az oyb oyb di komune darf oyszen azoy vi pan Gustav,

00:16:00.925 --> 00:16:08.411
azoy vi mayn man, er hot geheysn Godl Gustav oyf poylish. in gesheft hot men im gerufn di ale Gustav.

00:16:09.109 --> 00:16:14.081
UNK komune, zol lebn di komune. dos heyst az zi iz shoyn gevorn a komunistke.

00:16:14.290 --> 00:16:20.055
zi hot untergeshikt dem Kshevitski az zi vil im nemen. er hot nisht gevolt geyn.

00:16:19.639 --> 00:16:22.046
er hot nisht gevolt. far vos?

00:16:20.584 --> 00:16:21.354
neyn.

00:16:22.272 --> 00:16:29.336
far vos? far ikh ken aykh nisht zogn vos der mentsh hot gefilt, er volt nisht oysgehaltn gornisht.

00:16:25.647 --> 00:16:26.653
vos hot er gezogt?

00:16:29.865 --> 00:16:35.681
er hot gehat a rut un an energisher, alts bin ikh alts hob ikh untergenumen.

00:16:36.025 --> 00:16:44.321
m'hot im azoy vi a shlimazl dafke gef- opgestrashet m'vet im m'vet im shisn, m'hot im nisht geshosn un ikh hob nisht gelozt arop in gas arayn.

00:16:44.884 --> 00:16:52.201
er iz geven keseyder in di tsvey heyf. er hot gefirt dos hoyf, tsum ersht iz geven der s- in dem hoyf iz gevezn

00:16:52.815 --> 00:16:58.187
vu undz hobn gevoynt, dos private hoyf, iz geven tsvey heyf, un s'iz gevezn

00:16:58.187 --> 00:17:02.799
un ven m'hot aroysgeyogt di yidn fun derlebn, iz geven bay tsvey hundert lokatorn.

00:17:02.940 --> 00:17:08.033
un dernokh iz gornisht geblibn. tsum ersht hot zikh yeder eyner gekent epes koyfn, hot epes gehat,

00:17:08.033 --> 00:17:13.667
epes eyner a yid iz gekumen hot er geveynt, zogt er, panye, panye heyst in

00:17:13.723 --> 00:17:17.328
oyb s'a man pan, un oyb s'a froy panye zogt men.

00:17:17.487 --> 00:17:22.510
zogt, azoy hot men im, di yidn hobn azoy geredt panye, panye Roznboym tsu mayn man.

00:17:22.515 --> 00:17:27.633
ikh ken makhn tsukerlekh. s'shoyn nisht geven fun vemen tsu nemen keyn groshn.

00:17:27.633 --> 00:17:37.193
far oyf toyte tsu bagrobn iz shoyn nisht geven, tsu gebn an optsol. m'hot shoyn ale aroysgeleygt in droysn. ale zenen oysgeshtorbn toyterheyt toy- in UNK.

00:17:37.193 --> 00:17:48.666
kumen der yid, s'nisht geven bay tsu nemen keyn gelt. un ikh ikh hob gebrengt vos ikh hob fardint in shtub, zenen tsugegangen esn tsu elef mentshn tsum bisl zup mitn shtikl broyt.

00:17:48.874 --> 00:17:52.513
elef mentshn hobn gegesn bay aykh in shtub?

00:17:51.507 --> 00:17:54.656
mitog. mitog, nor mitog.

00:17:52.587 --> 00:17:54.640
mit ver, ver?

00:17:55.506 --> 00:17:58.655
mayn tateshi, mayn mameshi, un zey hobn gevoynt derlebn.

00:17:59.218 --> 00:18:06.080
un di tsvey meydlekh, a meydl vos hot gekokht un geroymt, un dos meydl tsum kind, un undz tsvey un dos kind.

00:18:07.116 --> 00:18:09.101
un eyn un an alte froy.

00:18:09.748 --> 00:18:12.695
un dos fun ales fun vos ir hot geshaft.

00:18:09.816 --> 00:18:17.044
hob ikh UNK. nor a bisl zup, yo, nor a bisl zup hobn zey gegesn. fun dem hot men gelebt.

00:18:17.044 --> 00:18:20.121
un dos meydl iz dafke geven fun a frumer heym.

00:18:20.177 --> 00:18:25.504
nor a sakh kinder, un hot gelebt gevoynt in a in a hoyz keygn iber.

00:18:25.543 --> 00:18:27.916
ikh darf a efsher oyfhern? red.

00:18:26.455 --> 00:18:28.153
neyn neyn, UNK.

00:18:29.138 --> 00:18:30.414
HAIKAR,

00:18:31.618 --> 00:18:34.227
er hot nisht gevolt geyn tsu di shikse.

00:18:33.255 --> 00:18:38.952
nisht gevolt geyn. iz iz bashlosn gevorn az s'zol vayter gefirt vern un vos vet zikh lozn.

00:18:39.330 --> 00:18:45.027
un ikh bin dervayle geganen ahin oyf Shliske tsu dem Kshevitski bin mit zey geshlofn.

00:18:45.709 --> 00:18:48.926
un dos iz vi lang ken men azoy shlofn mit a porfolk?

00:18:49.101 --> 00:18:50.833
un zi hot gearbet

00:18:51.109 --> 00:18:58.831
iz geven a shpitol fun kinder in Varshe, hot es geheysn DZIECIATKA JEZUS. s'heyst dos kind fun Yezusen.

00:18:59.007 --> 00:19:04.231
oyfn nomen fun ki- DZIECIATKA, DZIECIATKA heyst a kleyn kind, a pitsele kind.

00:19:04.440 --> 00:19:06.982
iz geven far a kinder shpitol.

00:19:07.191 --> 00:19:14.306
hot zi zeyer fil geholfn di vos zenen geven gemalet, az m'zol zikh makhn andersh,

00:19:14.903 --> 00:19:20.550
un heyst s'zol azoy vi nisht gemalet, un hot opgeratevet a sakh yidishe kinder.

00:19:20.758 --> 00:19:24.093
zi hot gearbet in dem shpitol, nisht als doktorin,

00:19:22.345 --> 00:19:27.097
Kshevitski's vay- zi iz geven Kshivyets- Kshevyitski's vay- froy.

00:19:25.011 --> 00:19:29.156
Kshevyitski's froy. yo. zayn froy iz dos geven.

00:19:29.871 --> 00:19:34.980
zi iz geven tsvey mol azoy groys vi er. er iz nisht geven keyn za hoykher, zi iz geven a hoykh, a dike.

00:19:34.980 --> 00:19:39.686
un ikh hob badorfn shlofn mit ir, un mit zey beyde in eyn- tsi iz dos ayngenem?

00:19:40.165 --> 00:19:47.671
HAIKAR, hot zikh ongehoybn farinteresirn, hot er iz ge- un iz

00:19:47.671 --> 00:19:52.275
er hot dokh bemeyle zenen zey geven UNK untergrunt, er iz dokh nisht geven keyn antisemit,

00:19:52.517 --> 00:19:58.771
hot er zikh f- hot er gekent ay- dem invalid fun di poylishe invalid, a in- a eyneme

00:19:58.896 --> 00:20:04.155
vos hot ge- Dorsht hot er geheysn, dem nomen gedenk ikh nisht.

00:20:04.498 --> 00:20:14.229
hot er gehat a a hiltserne fus fun di milkhome fun tsvontsikstn yor mit di Bolshevikes, hot Poyln gehat dem a milkhome, ven s'shoyn geven di Bolshevikes.

00:20:14.303 --> 00:20:20.169
iz er gevorn a invalid, un er hot geganen oyf aza oyf a,

00:20:20.918 --> 00:20:25.715
biz danet vayzt oys hot er nisht gehat dem fus, vayl do do hot arayngeshtekt

00:20:25.715 --> 00:20:30.834
biz un fun danet on efsher yo, ikh hob dokh nisht gezen, nor ikh farshtey az azoy iz gevezn.

00:20:31.701 --> 00:20:41.854
iz un er er hot er im gekent, un zenen geven a a kinderloz porfolk un zey hobn gevoynt vayt in Prage, iber di Vaysl.

00:20:42.771 --> 00:20:49.700
er iz glaykh ayngeganen. er hot im gezogt er hot aza un aza froy, un er vil tsoln, az er vil tsoln,

00:20:49.757 --> 00:20:55.910
un s'k- iberik iz gornisht geven, er hot dokh nisht gekent arbetn, un zi iz geven in shtub mit tsvey hint,

00:20:56.440 --> 00:21:03.470
un tsvey tsimern mit a shtub zenen geven ayngeordnt, geven iz er zikher in untergrunt.

00:21:04.253 --> 00:21:09.630
alzo, er iz ayngeganen, un zi hot mikh aribergefirt iber di brik.

00:21:10.176 --> 00:21:13.376
ikh bin ir nokhgeganen, ikh hob nisht gevust vu dos iz.

00:21:14.040 --> 00:21:21.594
un ikh bin bay im gevezn a sheyne por vokhn.

00:21:21.634 --> 00:21:26.791
ikh hob gegesn dos zelbe vos zey, un ikh hob gemakht dos zelbe mit di mogn.

00:21:27.523 --> 00:21:36.056
vayl in Poyln iz geven fir fayerkes azelkhe mine dos o. di drite fa- fayerke dortn, s'hot badorfn aropgeyn dos fayer mitn royekh,

00:21:36.214 --> 00:21:39.667
dortn hob ikh arayngerukt. azoy hob ikh mir an eytse gegebn.

00:21:39.707 --> 00:21:51.024
un zi hot genumen di tsvey hint, zi iz aropgeganen. oder zi hot genumen nisht di hint, zi hot mikh ibergelozt mit di hint, hobn zey zikh ongehoybn shlogn beyde, hobn zey gevolt mikh, vayl zey hobn gezen mikh keseyder veynen un raysn di hor fun kop.

00:21:51.199 --> 00:21:53.929
di nervn hobn shoyn nokh nisht gearbet, nor vos?

00:21:53.929 --> 00:21:59.659
ikh bin geshlofn in mitl shtub oyf aza bar, azoy vi a mentsh, un gegesn dos zelbe vos zey.

00:21:59.659 --> 00:22:06.482
zey hobn gegesn broyt mit puter mit kave, mir dos zelbe. un er hot gekrign getsolt.

00:22:09.036 --> 00:22:20.792
biz er hot ongehoybn zogn az, zi hot zi iz geven a alte mentsh, a kinderloze fun a dorf epes, un er hot gemuzt zayn, er er er hot gehat a biblyotek, er hot gehat a poylishe biblyotek, ikh hob geleyent bay im.

00:22:21.270 --> 00:22:27.423
hot er, un er iz geven a sekretar fun di invalidn, iz er dokh nisht gevezn keyn, iz geven keyn analfabet.

00:22:30.194 --> 00:22:36.873
BEKHEN az dey az Rublevski do vos kind iz, zukht mikh arum, er vil mir op dos kind

00:22:37.318 --> 00:22:41.868
dos iz geven der terets az zi ken er ken mikh nisht haltn mer.

00:22:45.283 --> 00:22:55.537
bin ikh tsurikgeganen arayn in geto arayn, in may. biz s'iz a- biz s'iz gevezn di WYSIEDLENIE.

00:22:57.282 --> 00:23:02.912
zey zey hot men gehat bazunder, zey hobn geshtelt a vidershtand, fir vokh- fir fir teg,

00:23:03.458 --> 00:23:07.080
do vu mayn man hot gehat di gute shnayders, oyf Leshno.

00:23:07.120 --> 00:23:13.428
ikh bin dokh nisht geven dos, nor mayn bruder iz geganen, s'geven punkt oyf peysekh, iz er gegan in geto arayn.

00:23:13.428 --> 00:23:18.201
der a bruder vos iz geven a yor mit elter mit mir, Avrom Pinkhes vos er shraybt.

00:23:18.578 --> 00:23:23.393
veys ikh nisht tsi er iz umgekumen in geto, tsi m'hot im aroysgefirt in a lager.

00:23:23.393 --> 00:23:25.811
vu er iz umgekumen veys ikh nisht.

00:23:26.475 --> 00:23:31.312
er iz, ikh veys nisht tsi er hot gehert tsum untergrunt, tsi zey m'hot geven in kontakt,

00:23:31.622 --> 00:23:38.062
tsi er iz geganen nokh a froy epes zukhn, er iz in a froy geven, di froy iz shoyn nisht gevezn, er iz geven a a yunger mentsh.

00:23:38.727 --> 00:23:40.867
veys ikh nisht vu er iz umgekumen.

00:23:40.867 --> 00:23:49.489
alzo, s'iz s'hot zikh ongerukt di tsayt, un s'hot badorfn zay- iz gevezn m'hot zey badorfn shikn. in gantsn vinter

00:23:49.489 --> 00:23:57.097
hot er hobn zey untergehandlt tsu forn, az s'vet zayn gute badingungen, zey veln gebn eygene dires, m'vet alding in Ponyatov.

00:23:57.357 --> 00:23:59.680
nor Varshe muz vern opgereynikt.

00:24:00.057 --> 00:24:08.857
hobn zey nisht a- a- ayngeganen keseyder. untergehandlt, vider geshmirt, vider gemakht matones, vider azoy vider azoy, azoy yener mit a groys ⟨optebers⟩.

00:24:08.857 --> 00:24:11.557
oyf nokh a gas iz oykh geven oyf ⟨Valitsu Vatebers⟩.

00:24:11.557 --> 00:24:14.977
un der fun Tebers fun undz fun undzer gas fun Leshno,

00:24:14.979 --> 00:24:21.211
un mit undz, nu do iz dokh geven oysgeshtelt nor oyf gebn matones, fun dest vegn hobn zikh gemuzt tsushteln.

00:24:21.336 --> 00:24:27.371
un er hot Itepers hot gezogt zayn vort az zey vet gornisht feln, s'vet zey nisht feln keyn hor fun kop.

00:24:28.170 --> 00:24:29.699
ikh bin geven bahaltn.

00:24:30.178 --> 00:24:34.492
ikh hob ge- dos iz geven numer fertsik hobn undz gearbet, hot hot hobn zey gearbet.

00:24:34.600 --> 00:24:41.056
un in tsvey un fertsik iz geven a bazar, a durkhgangs hoyf. dort hob ikh gevust fun a bunker.

00:24:41.586 --> 00:24:47.824
un er hot oykh gevust, mayn man. er iz nisht gevezn, er hot gevust vu s'iz geven mit a por monat tsurik, a bunker.

00:24:49.011 --> 00:24:53.530
in der heykh hot zikh gekhovet a a in a gevelb, a ferd,

00:24:53.530 --> 00:24:58.101
nor nisht in di tsayt, di ven dos iz geven nisht nor, koydem geshafn dem bunker.

00:24:58.512 --> 00:25:03.858
ikh bin dortn gevezn, ikh hob nisht gehat bedeye tsu forn. un ikh hob im im oykh opgeredt.

00:25:03.858 --> 00:25:08.985
"lomir zikh aroyskrign! m- Ktshevitski vet shoyn epes shafn far undz.

00:25:09.177 --> 00:25:13.603
vestu geyn", zog ikh, "tsu di shikse", ikh hob fargesn vi azoy zi hot geheysn, s'nisht vikhtik.

00:25:13.603 --> 00:25:19.441
ikh vel geyn tsu Ktshevitski, vet Tsh- Ktshevitski shoyn mir im epes shafn. un az nisht, iz nisht.

00:25:19.441 --> 00:25:23.649
ikh darf un s'iz vider toyt. ikh gleyb nisht Tebesn, ikh gleyb nisht gornisht.

00:25:24.246 --> 00:25:29.876
un ikh bin ikh hob, s'hot gornisht geholfn, ikh bin vider geforn mit im.

00:25:29.950 --> 00:25:34.131
m'iz untergekumen a veg, s'hot gedoyert

00:25:34.131 --> 00:25:39.764
f- zeks teg biz m- zey hobn detsidirt zikh oyf yo, az zey veln forn keyn Ponyatov.

00:25:40.412 --> 00:25:44.003
undz ze'mir geforn mit di mashinen, mit alding.

00:25:44.003 --> 00:25:48.737
iz di mashinen zenen geshtanen an ofene vagon, azoy vi m'firt beheymes.

00:25:48.737 --> 00:25:52.472
un undz ze'mir mit di mashinen geshtanen, nisht in keyn shum,

00:25:51.685 --> 00:25:54.699
ven iz dos geven? ir gedenkt a datum umgefer?

00:25:54.874 --> 00:26:02.749
dos iz gevezn in akhtsn a por un tsvontsikstn, efsher in finef un tsvontsikstn april.

00:26:02.856 --> 00:26:04.655
oder in zeks un tsvontsikstn.

00:26:04.425 --> 00:26:06.714
nayntsn dray un fertsik.

00:26:06.366 --> 00:26:10.427
yo. geven nokh peysekh shoyn.

00:26:12.998 --> 00:26:16.316
un mayn man iz epes gegebn a UNK zikh.

00:26:16.558 --> 00:26:23.201
un ikh kum on un ikh ze s'do epes a feld ful un do in di zayt iz do beymer, ikh veys nisht afilek vu.

00:26:24.051 --> 00:26:28.719
flink bin ikh geven vi a kats eybik, ikh hob gekent fararbetn shtendik fartsayen.

00:26:28.945 --> 00:26:35.351
shtendik iz bay mir alts farbrent gevorn, alts shnel. nisht vayl ikh, ikh hob aza natur, oyf shnel.

00:26:35.374 --> 00:26:38.912
un haynt ken ikh nebekh gornisht tun, meyle, vos zol ikh tun?

00:26:39.508 --> 00:26:41.577
un gegebn ikh bin gegebn a shprung arop.

00:26:42.816 --> 00:26:45.527
un ikh hob ongehoybn vandern, ikh hob aleyn nisht gevust vu,

00:26:44.183 --> 00:26:49.408
far vos hot ir gegebn a shprung arop? vos hot ir gezen, ir hot nisht gevolt.

00:26:46.562 --> 00:26:48.868
ikh hob nisht gevolt forn keyn Ponyatov.

00:26:49.195 --> 00:26:52.564
ikh hob dokh nisht gevolt in gantsn UNK, ikh bin dokh geven bahaltn vider.

00:26:53.312 --> 00:26:55.179
di zelbe vos farn kotsho.

00:26:55.438 --> 00:26:58.503
ikh hob mikh umetum gevolt, ikh hob gevust s'iz toyt.

00:26:58.560 --> 00:27:10.248
un do hob ikh shoyn a kind ergets, va- vos vet efsher iberlebn, vet dos blaybn, oder s'vet iberlebn vet es zayn on a mame, un ikh hob aleyn oykh gevolt lebn, vi yung, ikh bin dokh geven azoy yung.

00:27:11.048 --> 00:27:14.200
azoy rizedik, un a gezu- un gezunt oykhet.

00:27:14.200 --> 00:27:17.775
ikh hob di gantse tsayt fun dem geto nisht gehat keyn katar afile.

00:27:20.869 --> 00:27:28.085
aldos ikh hob ongehoybn vandern, vu ikh hob gekent, epes ikh hob gevandert dakht zikh alts dray tog.

00:27:28.277 --> 00:27:32.388
ikh bin tsurik ongekumen oyf Stalarski, tsu dem on fis.

00:27:35.888 --> 00:27:39.240
zi hot mikh, vayl keyner hot nisht gekent gevolt gevolt hobn.

00:27:39.550 --> 00:27:44.558
hot zi geshikt nokh dem Kshevitski, nisht zi hot nisht geshikt, zey hobn zikh getrofn,

00:27:44.558 --> 00:27:53.320
der on fis mit dem Kshevitski, vayl in Vodle- bay Rublevski oykhet, er hot dokh gemakht papirn ke- kemkartn, pasportn

00:27:53.341 --> 00:27:57.501
falshe far di vos zenen geven oyf di, hobn badorfn, afilek polyakn

00:27:57.501 --> 00:28:03.061
zenen geven mankhe vos vos di daytshn hobn gezukht, hobn oykh gehat falshe peser.

00:28:04.086 --> 00:28:12.635
un ikh bin dortn gevezn epes a p- tsvey tog, un s'gekumen di froy zayne, Kshevitski's froy,

00:28:13.300 --> 00:28:23.773
un un s'nokh geven a gelegnheyt. punkt hot men demolts bombardirt a vokzal in Vilner v- in Viner Vilner vokzal hot es geheysn DWORZEC WILENSKI.

00:28:24.690 --> 00:28:31.249
iz geven a bisl farvundete, fun dem bombardirn. di rusn hobn bombardirt shoyn.

00:28:31.356 --> 00:28:33.850
oder di englender, ikh veys nisht ver.

00:28:33.850 --> 00:28:40.833
ober der DWORZEC iz gevorn, der vakzal iz gevorn in Prage un s'iz gevezn a bisl farvundete.

00:28:41.751 --> 00:28:50.334
a klal, hob ikh mikh azoy arumgeviklt, s'shoyn gevezn a sakh vos hobn gekukt in di oygn arayn, hobn shoyn derkent di yidn oykhet, hobn zey geheysn kop- kote,

00:28:50.425 --> 00:28:56.173
Zhebratsha vos, farshidene mies- nemen hobn di yidn derkent.

00:28:56.550 --> 00:29:01.539
un zi hot mikh avekgefirt ergets sof fun varshe.

00:29:01.663 --> 00:29:08.292
vos ikh hob keyn mol nisht gehert dem nomen, m'hot es gerufn a tsunomen, s'hobn gevoynt unterveltnikes, banditn,

00:29:08.292 --> 00:29:14.229
hot es geheysn Nabudakh, tsu a porfolk vos ikh hob im gehat bakent.

00:29:14.455 --> 00:29:17.034
vegn zi hot gehat tsugenumen, di goye,

00:29:17.034 --> 00:29:22.931
a kind vos iz gevorn geboyrn, s'alt geven zeks vokhn oyf di WYSIEDLENIE, hobn zey es male gevezn.

00:29:22.931 --> 00:29:26.543
un er iz gevezn eyner vos iz geven oyf di Makabyade do,

00:29:26.543 --> 00:29:31.892
er iz geven a instruktor fun shimen fun Makabi in Varshe.

00:29:31.892 --> 00:29:34.614
MAS- LEHAFSIK?

00:29:37.253 --> 00:29:40.776
hobn zey gehat a kind, er hot epes khasene gehat mit a

00:29:40.776 --> 00:29:48.868
alte moyd epes, un zey hobn es, az zey zenen geven azoy klug az in azan bitere tsayt, s'nisht geven tsu esn nisht gornisht, hobn zey es male geven.

00:29:48.868 --> 00:29:55.247
nor er hot zikh bakent mit dem Kshevitski, un zi di froy hot dos kind genumen oykh in dem shpitelerl arayn.

00:29:55.247 --> 00:30:01.668
un s'dokh geven a yungitshke, azoy iz memeyle hot men gekent propra- un makhn im beser dos vos iz male gevezn.

00:30:01.553 --> 00:30:04.571
m'vet undz ve'mir vayter geyn oyf di nekste kaset.
